headline: Colgate-Palmolive (CL) Target Raised as Analysts Split on 2026 Staples Outlook
summary: Colgate-Palmolive Company (NYSE:CL) is included among the 14 Best Dividend Aristocrats to Invest in Heading into 2026. On December 19, BofA raised its price target on Colgate-Palmolive Company (NYSE:CL) to $90 from $88 and kept a Buy rating. Looking ahead to 2026, the firm said the biggest open question for consumer staples is still consumption […]
